divs: Sighting DetailsI was feeding my dog when I saw some unusual stars. but I looked and saw a craft hovering about 150 feet in the air. It was also above the treeline. And It was a stary and cloudy night but were the UFO was the clouds and stars were gone. IT WAS TOTALLY SIGHLENT!!!!!!!!! And it just huvored there for a little while then shot off and the treeline kept me from seeing any spacific direction. I first though it was an air plane, but they make noise and don't hover. It was the size of an SUV, and had 2 white round lights in the front of the bottom and 1 red one in the back of the bottom it also thad strips of white light bettwen the lights was black
